title: Detectives investigating after 2 people found dead in Lynnwood...
text:
Detectives are investigating after two people were found dead in a home in Lynnwood.
The bodies were discovered by a family member at a home in the 3100 block of 202 nd Street Southwest at about 3 p.m. Thursday.
Deputies say the deceased appeared to have gunshot wounds. They have not been identified.
Authorities are continuing their investigation.
